::Battera::

She sighed,"Yes you can.  I'll go outside and wait for you there.  
I'm at the Cybertron Fire."

She sighed and got up.  She walked back into the rooma nd looked at 
Prowl and Iron Raptor. "I have a friend coming to assist me. May he 
be allowed to enter your base?  He is CyberShark.  He too is trying 
to help in getting the peace talks organized." 


--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, "David Torrey" <Dachande85@m...> wrote:
> ::CyberShark::
> 
>     He only recived this part of the message. "But where will they 
be-----" The rest was static. He tried to send a message through to 
her. "I'm in the Destron base as of now, I don't think that I'm going 
to be able to get through the static for a while."
>     Magmatron's holo image still was before him, just staring. 
CyberShark turned and left, he didn't know who Magmatron had left in 
charge, but he hoped it wasn't Bobertron.
>     He left the base and did a quick scan for the Temporal Gate. He 
found it.
>     "Battera, Magmatron left the planet," CyberShark said, sure 
that the static wouldn't affect the comm system once outside of the 
Destron base. "He said for me to go through it and join him, but 
don't worry I'm not gonna. Can I join you at the Maximal base?"
